tes av styret, s\u00e5 det m\u00e5 du sp\u00f8rre styreleder om.", "If\u00f8lge \u00e5rsrapporten hadde Haugan en fastl\u00f8nn p\u00e5 3,73 millioner kroner i fjor, mot 3,47 millioner \u00e5ret f\u00f8r. Det tilsvarer en l\u00f8nns\u00f8kning p\u00e5 cirka 7 prosent.", "\u2013 Bortfallet av bonuser er ikke kompensert med h\u00f8yere i fastl\u00f8nn, men det kan hende at noen vil f\u00e5 en h\u00f8yere grunnl\u00f8nnsutvikling enn de ellers ville f\u00e5tt, sier styreleder Bjordal til Adressa.no.", "B\u00e5rd Ove Molberg950 21 523baard.ove.molberg@adresseavisen.no"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "eacaeab44d606dee7b8985736ab6d34eeba0896392d9704fc934c479aa9d6835"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-01-17T08:41:23.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "SMN-sjef Finn Haugan vinket farvel til halve bonusen i fjor."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/okonomi/article9370969.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Haugan.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/553975699b888194b7196f20172f9cca41460a8e.jpg?592184b8"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Ble med p\u00e5 \u00abspleiselaget\u00bb -adressa.no", "\u2013 En omd\u00f8mmeutfordring", "Sju prosent l\u00f8nns\u00f8kning"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "553975699b888194b7196f20172f9cca41460a8e"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "personal-finance"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["bonus", "millioner kroner"]}, {"field": "kw-entity",